<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <title>Chapter 1: Introduction</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Chapter 1: Introduction</h1>
    <p>Welcome to this sample EPUB book created for testing the Literati AI reading companion application.</p>
    
    <p>This is a simple test book that contains:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Basic EPUB 3.0 structure</li>
        <li>Valid metadata</li>
        <li>Navigation document</li>
        <li>Sample content</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>The purpose of this book is to test the EPUB upload functionality in Literati, ensuring that:</p>
    <ol>
        <li>File validation works correctly</li>
        <li>Metadata extraction functions properly</li>
        <li>Content processing operates as expected</li>
        <li>Database storage completes successfully</li>
    </ol>
    
    <p>If you can read this text after uploading, then the basic EPUB processing is working correctly!</p>
    
    <h2>About Literati</h2>
    <p>Literati is an AI-powered reading companion that helps users understand and interact with complex literature through contextual assistance, character tracking, and historical context.</p>
    
    <p>This sample book will help test the foundation of that experience.</p>
</body>
